messages.content: That's an odd question to ask, Tally. But to answer, no, I'm not black. I'm Greek, as my name might suggest. Is there a reason you were curious about my ethnicity?
messages.speaker: Gregor Mastori

messages.content: You looked black from a distance
messages.speaker: Tally

messages.content: Ah, I see. Well, appearances can be deceiving, as they say. But regardless of my ethnicity, I'm here to do my job as a journalist and document the situation on the island. Is there anything I can help you with, Tally?
messages.speaker: Gregor Mastori

messages.content: Alright then, take care and stay safe out there, Tally. If you need anything in the future or if you have any questions about what I'm doing here, don't hesitate to ask. Good luck on your mission.
messages.speaker: Gregor Mastori
